      "packet_type": "result",
      "title": "Compared the current homepage against the upstream conference template and found that the largest alignment gaps are the hero/banner treatment, the navigation rhythm, and several homepage-only CSS customizations that replace the template\u2019s plain content flow with a more custom landing-page look. The minimum Builder change set is to restore the template\u2019s image-backed banner and navigation proportions, then keep the ATLAS copy while removing the custom callout styling rather than rewriting content.",
